    fire_spirit: "fire-header{Flame Explosion}<br>DMG: fire{%{attr1}} of ATK x number of Fire-type Cookies<br>Flame Explosion Periodic DMG: x7 over 3.5 sec, fire{%{attr2}} DMG per hit<br>DMG Resist Bypass: 40.0%<br>status{Explosive_Burn} fire-header{Explosive Burn}<br>DMG: fire{53.6%} DMG every 0.25 sec for 6 sec<br>Fire-type DMG: +45.0%<br>Stacks up to x2<br>DMG Resist Bypass: 40.0%<br>fire-header{Fire Orb}<br>DMG: fire{499.6%} of ATK<br>Chain Explosion DMG: fire{388.1%} of ATK x number of Fire-type Cookies<br>DMG Resist Bypass: 40.0%<br>status{Weakness|und_debuff} Weakness: +30.0% for 20 sec; stacks up to x1<br>fire-header{Wall of Fire}<br>Applies stack x5 to allies at the beginning of battle<br>status{HP_Shield} HP Shield: 7.0% of Max HP x number of Fire-type Cookies for 7 sec<br>DMG Resist per HP Shield: +8.0%<br>fire-header{Unquenchable Flames}<br>status{Revive|und_buff} Revival: revived once with 70.0% HP, Cooldown Reset, 2 sec status{Invulnerable|und_buff} Invulnerability if defeated in battle<br>Flame Hydra: 213.6% of summoner's ATK, withstands x25 hits<br>Max x5 summoned for 10 sec<br>Flame Hydra DMG: fire{335.4%} of ATK x number of Fire-type Cookies<br>Flame Hydra Burn: fire{91.1%} of ATK every 1 sec for 5 sec; stacks up to x5<br>header{Number of Fire-type Ally Cookies}<br>1 Cookie x color{fire:1.05 times}<br>2 Cookies x color{fire:1.07 times}<br>3 Cookies x color{fire:1.10 times}<br>4 Cookies x color{fire:2.75 times}<br>5 Cookies x color{fire:3.00 times}<br>6 Cookies x color{fire:3.50 times}",
